# Operation Deep Clean - C:\ Drive Analysis

## Objective
Free up minimum 100 GB on C:\ drive (currently 96% full - 892/931 GB used)

## Phase 1: Gaming Scan
- [ ] Scan Program Files for game clients
- [ ] Scan Program Files (x86) for game clients
- [ ] Scan root C:\ for Games/XboxGames folders
- [ ] List all gaming installations with sizes

## Phase 2: Ghost Apps Scan
- [ ] Scan for Adobe Creative Cloud installations
- [ ] Scan for DaVinci Resolve
- [ ] Scan for Visual Studio old versions
- [ ] Scan for Android Studio
- [ ] Check AppData\Local for heavy caches
- [ ] Check AppData\Roaming for heavy caches

## Phase 3: Forgotten Files Scan
- [ ] Scan Downloads folder for files > 1GB
- [ ] Scan Desktop for files > 1GB
- [ ] Identify ISO, ZIP, RAR, 7Z, EXE, MP4, MKV files
- [ ] Check root C:\ for suspicious folders (Backup, Copy, Old)

## Reporting
- [ ] Generate deletion candidates list
- [ ] Generate migration candidates list
